Numis Asset Management (NAM)
NAM is a specialist asset manager that aims to provide investors access to a range of investment processes. We aim to deliver performance by devoting specialist resource to our asset selection process. Our maiden fund is the FP Numis UK Mid-Cap Fund.
Our People

James Hamilton – Executive Director & Fund Manager
Simon King – Executive Director & Fund Manager
Simon Denyer – Executive Director

Our Philosophy

We do not invest in what we do not understand: Active stock selection is made by industry experts.
We believe outperformance comes from information and knowledge asymmetry: We only actively invest where we believe we have a substantial knowledge advantage.
We do more work on each investment: We build detailed bottom up forecasts and valuations for every company we cover
Low and transparent charges: We aim to offer better value.




