Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Institutional Financial Svcs
Sub-Industry: Institutional Brokerage
Numis Securities Inc. operates as a broker dealer. The Company offers brokerage services, support structure, and other financial services. Numis Securities serves clients in the United States.




