July 24, 2017 1:33 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Numis Securities Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Numis Securities Inc. operates as a broker-dealer. It offers sales and trading services to institutional clients. The company also distributes research reports in the United States. The company was founded in 2003 and is based in New York, New York. Numis Securities Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Numis Securities Limited.


275 Madison AvenueSuite 4100New York, NY 10016United StatesFounded in 2003



Phone: 212-277-7300

www.numiscorp.com/x/us/default.html?rc=US







