Home > About Us
About Us
Listed on AIM and with offices in London and New York, Numis has grown to become one of the UK's most respected institutional stockbrokers and corporate advisors. We employ circa 200 staff, and the group is listed on AIM.













Legal and Regulatory conditions governing this website

Numis Securities Ltd is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority (Firm Reference Number 144822).

Numis Securities Inc is a registered US broker-dealer and Member 
FINRA / 
SIPC.

Numis Asset Management Ltd is authorised and regulated by the 
Financial Conduct Authority
(Firm Reference Number 612473).











